expressions.name: getLoopbackSenderProperties
expressions.body:
let loopback : OsIocSenderProperties = osIocSenderProperties
					->any(osIocSendingOsApplication = self.osIocReceiverProperties.osIocReceivingOsApplication)

					endif

expressions.name: getSwAddrMethod
expressions.body:
let implType : m2::ImplementationDataType = getImplementationDataType() , applType : m2::ApplicationDataType
					= getApplicationDataType()
				in if not self.prototype.swAddrMethod.oclIsUndefined()
						then self.prototype.swAddrMethod

						then implType.swAddrMethod
					else if not implType.getLeafImplementationDataType().swAddrMethod.oclIsUndefined()

expressions.name: getSwImplPolicy
expressions.body:

					= getApplicationDataType()
				in if not applType.getSwImplPolicy().oclIsUndefined() and applType.getSwImplPolicy() <> m2::SwImplPolicyEnum::unspecified
						then applType.getSwImplPolicy()
					else if not implType.getSwImplPolicy().oclIsUndefined() and implType.getSwImplPolicy() <> m2::SwImplPolicyEnum::unspecified
						then implType.getSwImplPolicy()
					else self.prototype.getSwImplPolicy()
					endif endif
